# Introduction
Enables the copying of content from 3rd party storage providers into Intralinks.
# Example Request JSON
The 'source' and 'destination' each must be a fully qualified URI. In the case where Dropbox is the source, we also
support public links for individual files. Here are some examples requests:
```json
{
  "source": [
    {
      "url": "/v1/il-storage/accounts/12345/cdmi_objectid/skd37Dh9O"
    }
  ],
  "destination": {
    "url": "/via/v1/workspaces/54321/folders/98765"
  }
}
```
```json
{
  "source": [
    {
      "url": "/v1/il-storage/accounts/12345/cdmi_objectid/skd37Dh9O"
    }
  ],
  "destination": {
    "url": "/v2/workspaces/54321/folders/98765"
  }
}

```
```json
{
  "source": [
    {
      "url": "https://www.dropbox.com/s/9uszp676lso3xca/git-cmd.png?dl=0"
    }
  ],
  "destination": {
    "url": "/v2/workspaces/54321/folders/98765"
  }
}
```
# Examples With 'asset' Parameter:
```json
{
  "source": [
    {
      "asset": {
        "workspaceId": 12345,
        "id": 54321,
        "kind": "document"
      }
    }
  ],
  "destination": {
    "url": "/v1/il-storage/accounts/12345"
  }
}
```
```json
{
  "source": [
    {
      "url": "/v1/il-storage/accounts/12345/cdmi_objectid/skd37Dh9O"
    }
  ],
  "destination": {
    "asset": {
      "workspaceId": 12345,
      "id": 54321,
      "kind": "folder"
    }
  }
}
```
